snippet: The Minnesota Vikings have completed an agreement with the University of Minnesota to play their home games at TCF Bank Stadium while the new Vikings stadium is being built.
abstract: Minnesota Vikings complete an agreement with the University of Minnesota to play their home games at TCF Bank Stadium while the new Vikings stadium is being built; other football news noted.
